Category_cols = ["Department", "Gender", "JobRole", "EducationField", "MaritalStatus", "OverTime", "BusinessTravel", "JobInvolvement", "JobSatisfaction", "WorkLifeBalance", "DistanceFromHome"]
for i in Category_cols:
    plt.figure(figsize = (8,6))
    sns.countplot(data= Hr_analytics, hue="Attrition", palette='rocket', x=i)
    plt.title(f"Attrition by {i}")
    plt.xticks(ha='left', rotation=45)
    plt.show()
